cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with multi-label classification using deep learning techniques, specifically for emotion classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the end-to-end learning framework, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses text as input, which suggests the possibility of cs.CV (Computer Vision) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval) categories. Finally, the paper proposes a new model for multi-label classification, which can be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
